<paragraph id="267936C4FE42FF89FF0AF91E5D90F95E" blockId="2.[166,1225,1711,1866]" box="[219,470,1743,1770]" pageId="2" pageNumber="23">B i o l o g y. Unknown.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="267936C4FE42FF89FF0AF93E583AF8FD" blockId="2.[166,1225,1711,1866]" pageId="2" pageNumber="23">
D i a g n o s t i c c h a r a c t e r s: Antenna yellow, arista with white hairs (figs 1, 
<emphasis id="14B2EAD6FE42FF89FB9EF9215830F8BE" box="[1103,1142,1775,1801]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="23">b, c</emphasis>
); wing pattern as in 
<figureCitation id="BEFD2A41FE42FF89FE96F8C15DECF89E" box="[327,426,1807,1833]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="3.[174,207,943,965]" captionTargetBox="[197,1164,178,924]" captionTargetId="figure-305@3.[193,1176,174,936]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="Fig. 1. Euthycera sticticaria (Mayer, 1953): a — female habitus (lateral view); b — head (lateral view, male); c — antennal (lateral view, male); d — sternites 5 and 6 in male, e — sternite 5 (ventral view of abdomen, male); f — Epandrium and surstylus (caudal view, male)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6404174" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6404174/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="23">Figure 1</figureCitation>
, 
<emphasis id="14B2EAD6FE42FF89FE6BF8DE5D8EF89E" box="[442,456,1808,1833]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="23">a</emphasis>
; sternite 5 with 2 small lobe at the middle (figs 1, 
<emphasis id="14B2EAD6FE42FF89FBFDF8C1587DF89E" box="[1068,1083,1807,1833]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="23">d</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis id="14B2EAD6FE42FF89FB9BF8DE5810F89E" box="[1098,1110,1808,1833]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="23">e</emphasis>
), sternite 6 with 2 flat and asymmetrical projection at middle (fig. 1, 
<emphasis id="14B2EAD6FE42FF89FC84F8E15F22F8FE" box="[853,868,1839,1865]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="23">d</emphasis>
), surstylus as in fig. 1, 
<emphasis id="14B2EAD6FE42FF89FBBCF8E15833F8FE" box="[1133,1141,1839,1865]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="23">f</emphasis>
.
</paragraph>
